Moved all classes into a package.
Implemented swing representation for displaying process.
Updated power usage logic to be used on move and not clean. Added exception for power level hitting 0. Added Tests for power usage.
Incremental changes for implementing instructions for the robot to return to charging station if it is running low on power.
